title: #92Noon! Bercich/Leber/Wobby
description: PA and Nordo are back at the TCO Performance Center with a cavalcade of football guests. Vikings Radio Network analyst Pete Bercich kicks things off, Ben Leber stops by, and Wobby dispels all rumors that he will be performing PA's colonoscopy!
